there's how many properties?

20
00:01:14.171 --> 00:01:17.652
I said right there,
there are about 350 properties.

21
00:01:17.652 --> 00:01:22.064
This is a lot like HTML,
that you really are only gonna use,

22
00:01:22.064 --> 00:01:26.138
