if ever going to use.

27
00:01:39.935 --> 00:01:44.241
So color, as you may imagine is
quite useful, we use it quite a bit.

28
00:01:44.241 --> 00:01:48.440
So color is going to
change the font color.

29
00:01:48.440 --> 00:01:50.216
